{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2460450/extras/Features.png?t=1714581731\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2460450/extras/Man_Divider.png?t=1714581731\" /><br>You\u2019ve been abducted and wake up in a man\u2019s basement. He tells you that he will kill you at midnight. A clock on the wall tells you that its 6pm. You have time find a way out, but this Man knows what he is doing. You\u2019ll need to learn from your mistakes, because he learns from his. Use items and unlock doors, all while avoiding the Man who adapts to your tactics.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Man</strong></h2>The man will adapt when you evade him, making you unable to use the same tactic twice.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2460450/extras/Man_CB1.gif?t=1714581731\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2460450/extras/Man_CB2.gif?t=1714581731\" /><br><br>Use whatever you can in the house, including the houses vents. But don't rely on them, the Man may be able to trap you..<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2460450/extras/Vents.gif?t=1714581731\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Time</strong></h2>You must escape before midnight. The only way to tell time is by looking at the clocks in his house. Every time you are knocked out, you are unconscious for 2 hours. If you wake up past midnight: it\u2019s game over.<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2460450/extras/Mind_Divider.png?t=1714581731\" /><br>You don\u2019t know where you are, how you got here, and what it going on. The only thing you know is that your daughter is in trouble. You need to find her, but you don\u2019t know how to do that either. Uncover the mystery and reclaim reality.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Puzzles</strong></h2>Solve mind-bending puzzles in order to progress through this psychological horror experience. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2460450/extras/Rooms.gif?t=1714581731\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2460450/extras/Doors.gif?t=1714581731\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Mystery</strong></h2>Something is going on, solve the puzzles to find out.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2460450/extras/Monster_Divider.png?t=1714581731\" /><br>You stumble upon an abandoned sewer treatment plant. You were just parkouring and looking for new territory, but you didn\u2019t expect to find what was lurking underground. Now you\u2019ll have to jump, swing, and climb to escape this monster.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Parkour</strong></h2>You'll need use your parkour skills to evade the monster, all while finding a way out. You'll need to get across one big gap by building a path.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2460450/extras/Swings_Jumps.gif?t=1714581731\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2460450/extras/Slides_Vault.gif?t=1714581731\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Mano a Mano","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2460450/dacb9a67481f8b938fe4114ef693caf4062e8dc0.jpg"},{"name":"Back Door","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2460450/48d8e26b66ed3ec85840ffdb7a50b0c44961919c.jpg"},{"name":"Meeting the Agents","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2460450/c06d150fc65d01735c739d82916741431b5dbf9f.jpg"},{"name":"Cerebral Assassin